import React from 'react'

import {
  ButtonHome,
  ButtonUser,
  ButtonTeam,
  ContainerTab,
  TabBar,
  ContainerButtons,
  ContainerVirtualButtons,
} from '../../styles/components/Navigation'

export const Navigation = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <ContainerTab>
        <ContainerButtons>
          <ContainerVirtualButtons>
            <ButtonTeam />
            <ButtonHome />
            <ButtonUser />
          </ContainerVirtualButtons>
        </ContainerButtons>
        <TabBar />
      </ContainerTab>
    </>
  )
}
